* &quot;Bad Boy&quot; (1997)
* &quot;You Make Me Free Make Me Fly!&quot; (1997)
* &quot;Holding Hands&quot; (1998)
* &quot;Can I Hug You, Lover?&quot; (1999)
* &quot;Regardless&quot; (2000)
* &quot;Journey&quot; (2001)
* &quot;Truth&quot; (2001)
* &quot;Fever&quot; (2002)
* &quot;Brave&quot; (2003)
* &quot;Maybe Tomorrow&quot; (2004)
* &quot;I Want Happiness?&quot; (2006)
* &quot;Star&quot; (2007)
* &quot;Amit&quot; (2009)
* &quot;R U Watching?&quot; (2011)
* &quot;Faces of Paranoia&quot; (2014)
* &quot;Amit 2&quot; (2015)
* &quot;Story Thief&quot; (2017)

