== International relations ==
=== Twin towns — sister cities ===

Nova Gorica is twinned with:

* Aleksandrovac, Serbia
* Klagenfurt, Austria
* Otočac, Croatia
* San Vendemiano, Italy
* Oghuz, Azerbaijan

